TEXT_HOUFIXCOMPANYSUBMARINE_00447_SUBMARINE_NAME_MES_0<tab>Names must be formed from alphanumeric characters. The following punctuation marks are also allowed:
<var 48 F201FC /var><var 49 F201FD /var>'<var 1D /var>. , : ; ! ? & - _<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var>
• Double spaces/underscores are not allowed.
• A space cannot be used before or after the name.
• Names consisting solely of punctuation marks are prohibited.

source: TEXT_HOUFIXCOMPANYSUBMARINE_00447_NO_REGISTRATION_1<tab>To outfit and register a submersible, you must have in your possession the requisite components and dive credits.
target: TEXT_HOUFIXCOMPANYSUBMARINE_00447_NO_REGISTRATION_1<tab>To outfit and register a submersible, you must have in your possession the requisite components and dive credits.

source: TEXT_HOUFIXCOMPANYSUBMARINE_00447_NO_REGISTRATION_2<tab><var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>Dive credits<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var> can be purchased from resident caretakers with company credits.
target: TEXT_HOUFIXCOMPANYSUBMARINE_00447_NO_REGISTRATION_2<tab><var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>Dive credits<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var> can be purchased from resident caretakers with company credits.

source: TEXT_HOUFIXCOMPANYSUBMARINE_00447_NO_REGISTRATION_3<tab><var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>Submersible components<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var> can be constructed in your company workshop. Please note that hull, stern, bow, and bridge components are required to outfit a submersible.
target: TEXT_HOUFIXCOMPANYSUBMARINE_00447_NO_REGISTRATION_3<tab><var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>Submersible components<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var> can be constructed in your company workshop. Please note that hull, stern, bow, and bridge components are required to outfit a submersible.

source: TEXT_HOUFIXCOMPANYSUBMARINE_00447_NO_ENERGY<tab>You cannot deploy your submersible on subaquatic voyages without ceruleum tanks, which can be purchased from resident caretakers with company credits.
target: TEXT_HOUFIXCOMPANYSUBMARINE_00447_NO_ENERGY<tab>You cannot deploy your submersible on subaquatic voyages without ceruleum tanks, which can be purchased from resident caretakers with company credits.

source: TEXT_HOUFIXCOMPANYSUBMARINE_00447_NO_EXPLOG_1<tab>Upon the completion of a subaquatic voyage, your mammet will provide a <var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>voyage log<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var> detailing the results.
target: TEXT_HOUFIXCOMPANYSUBMARINE_00447_NO_EXPLOG_1<tab>Upon the completion of a subaquatic voyage, your mammet will provide a <var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>voyage log<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var> detailing the results.

source: TEXT_HOUFIXCOMPANYSUBMARINE_00447_NO_EXPLOG_2<tab>The information contained in this log may prove useful in preparing for your next subaquatic voyage.
target: TEXT_HOUFIXCOMPANYSUBMARINE_00447_NO_EXPLOG_2<tab>The information contained in this log may prove useful in preparing for your next subaquatic voyage.

source: TEXT_HOUFIXCOMPANYSUBMARINE_00447_NO_EXPLOG_3<tab>Please note that only the log for the previous voyage will be retained.
target: TEXT_HOUFIXCOMPANYSUBMARINE_00447_NO_EXPLOG_3<tab>Please note that only the log for the previous voyage will be retained.

source: TEXT_HOUFIXCOMPANYSUBMARINE_00447_NO_REPAIR_ITEM<tab>You cannot repair submersible components without the requisite materials.
target: TEXT_HOUFIXCOMPANYSUBMARINE_00447_NO_REPAIR_ITEM<tab>You cannot repair submersible components without the requisite materials.
